                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I always melee and act as main looter in LDoNs.  Do I have any illusions of being a tank?  No.  But my proc DPS is better than none.  My better half (an enchanter) acts as puller and runs out of mana long before I ever do (unless he can find a caster to suck mana from) because he never gets to med.  I have no problem keeping people healed.  I am not watching the mob, I am watching health bars.  I know my job.
<br />

<br />
One thing you haven't mentioned is that even though sitting is slightly better mana regen than standing with yaulp V, when you stand up to cast complete heal, you have no mana regen going.  With yaulp, you can regen entirely through the cast.
<br />

<br />
I find that my mana flow is actually better when I tank with yaulp, then when I sit.
<br />

<br />
Also, I always get a clicky speed from my better half, but that's only because it doesn't take any mana to give it to me.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Ykina Zunderfoot, so please don't step on her
